Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.10,0:00:03.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Waiting gets us nowhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.42,0:00:04.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Take a step forward into the future...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.54,0:00:05.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Begin the deduction and love countdown!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.29,0:00:08.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The lawyer Kisaki Eri and the great detective Mouri Kogoro...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.75,0:00:10.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A fateful confrontation between a separated couple!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.76,0:00:12.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Perceiving the one and only truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.22,0:00:13.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A child with the intellect of an adult...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.88,0:00:15.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His name is: Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.42,0:02:01.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We had a dinner appointment with Ran's mother, the lawyer Kisaki Eri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.01,0:02:07.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,On the way to get her, we discovered the body of the popular fighter Nagasaku Shirou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.31,0:02:10.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,From the condition of the body...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.69,0:02:15.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seemed that Nagasaku{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} had been killed as he was getting his hair cut at a barber shop or beauty salon.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.24,0:02:20.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The one who ran a beauty parlor in the neighborhood, Hasaka Minayo{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.74,0:02:21.16,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Hasaka Minayo (29)\NBeautician
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.16,0:02:23.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Confirmed that she had been a former girlfriend of the victim.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.16,0:02:25.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Suspicion turned towards her, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.70,0:02:29.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,During the time it seemed that the crime was committed...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.83,0:02:32.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She had been caring for Kisaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r}'s hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.92,0:02:34.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If we presume Minayo{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was the culprit...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.96,0:02:38.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How could she have moved the 90 kg corpse to the garbage collection point?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.18,0:02:41.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When we discovered the body...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.72,0:02:43.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We heard them:
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.10,0:02:45.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A "whack," a "thud," and "klink klink."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.81,0:02:47.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What caused those three sounds?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.81,0:02:56.44,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,LAWYER KISAKI ERI'S TESTIMONY\N(PART TWO)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.78,0:02:57.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.57,0:03:00.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Everyone's going.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.20,0:03:01.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shall we go too?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.13,0:03:14.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why are those there?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.71,0:03:16.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That table and chair.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.63,0:03:18.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe she collected the things she wasn't using...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.92,0:03:21.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And put them out for the next bulk garbage collection.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.26,0:03:25.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But Minayo{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s really well-organized, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.93,0:03:27.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because look...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.35,0:03:31.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The newspapers and magazines have been properly separated.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.64,0:03:34.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the cardboard has been folded up in small pieces and tied too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.23,0:03:36.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.91,0:03:46.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.95,0:03:50.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You ride your scooter in this narrow alley?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.87,0:03:51.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.79,0:03:53.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Normally there's no one here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.00,0:03:58.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why does that guy keep calling?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.92,0:04:01.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't want to answer it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.30,0:04:06.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After all, it could be from that cute young lady at your favorite store.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.51,0:04:07.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.22,0:04:08.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.56,0:04:11.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why does it always end up this way?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.19,0:04:14.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's that convenience store over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.78,0:04:22.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So the garbage collection point where the body was opposite direction, tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.61,0:04:26.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The dust on the pole of this road sign.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.57,0:04:29.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Has been rubbed off, and there's a thin stripe.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.37,0:04:31.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where'd this stripe come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.50,0:04:37.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Cigarette butts other rubbish have been collected into a circle...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.67,0:04:40.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.01,0:04:45.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is this the place?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.93,0:04:50.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is the garbage collection point next to the convenience store where you went to throw out the garbage?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.31,0:04:52.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.81,0:04:54.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you people want something?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.02,0:04:57.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're in charge of this convenience store?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.86,0:04:58.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.02,0:05:01.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're with the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.15,0:05:03.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The police?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.78,0:05:04.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.28,0:05:07.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I heard there had been an incident in the neighborhood, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.53,0:05:10.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it pertains to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.53,0:05:13.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you know what time she came here tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.08,0:05:16.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Minayo{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}, you're under suspicion?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.62,0:05:18.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.46,0:05:21.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, we're only checking just in case.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.71,0:05:22.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.21,0:05:25.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I remember correctly, I think it was around 8:30 PM.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.47,0:05:28.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think we'd know if we looked at the shop's receipts...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.43,0:05:32.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since Minayo{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r} was the only who bought rice tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.39,0:05:37.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,8:28 PM, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.60,0:05:42.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you know how long she was in the store at that time?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.48,0:05:45.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I believe it was four or five minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.99,0:05:48.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We could find out for sure by checking the security camera.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.49,0:05:52.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If that's so, then isn't it totally impossible for her to be the culprit?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.99,0:05:56.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When she left me and stepped out for an errand, it was 8:20.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.50,0:06:00.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When she came back after finishing her errand, it was 8:30.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.83,0:06:05.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She arrived at this convenience store sometime between 8:23 and 8:24.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.67,0:06:08.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If she finished shopping and headed back at 8:28, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.01,0:06:13.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The time available for the crime was either the three or four minutes before coming to the convenience store...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.14,0:06:15.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Or the fewer than two minutes after she headed home.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.02,0:06:20.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's too little time to murder him and transport his body to the garbage collection point.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.52,0:06:27.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When she came to this store tonight, she was carrying a garbage bag, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.20,0:06:30.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, two or three of them...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.74,0:06:33.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And what if one of them didn't contain garbage, but a corpse instead?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.49,0:06:35.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh?! A corpse?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.45,0:06:36.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dear...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.29,0:06:38.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.37,0:06:41.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even though she could have been carrying a corpse on her scooter...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.21,0:06:42.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That'd have been impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.96,0:06:43.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Impossible?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.04,0:06:44.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's because...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.25,0:06:50.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The engine on Minayo{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}'s scooter sort of stalled and broke down before she got here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.84,0:06:51.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stalled?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.76,0:06:56.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, just when I had gone outside the store to put out the trash...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.02,0:07:00.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just as Minayo{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r} came out of the back alley that leads to her place...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.56,0:07:02.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I noticed it sputtered and stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.98,0:07:03.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After that...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.98,0:07:07.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She got off the scooter and pushed it by hand up to the store.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.03,0:07:11.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It fixed itself after I left it there for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.36,0:07:12.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I then rode it home.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.12,0:07:15.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you get it now?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.03,0:07:16.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's innocent.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.54,0:07:19.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Given that she's my treasured beautician...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.08,0:07:21.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could you please stop making accusations against her?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.46,0:07:24.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.17,0:07:26.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Keep on defending me...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.30,0:07:28.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Lawyer Kisaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.05,0:07:34.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There are some blond hairs sticking to your stomach.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.01,0:07:37.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,T-That can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.47,0:07:38.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I changed clothes properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.73,0:07:42.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now that I look closer, they're brown.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.27,0:07:45.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They must be Kisaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r}'s.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.81,0:07:47.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,R-Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.78,0:07:49.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That reaction...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.57,0:07:52.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She must be the culprit.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.49,0:07:54.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I don't get it...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.49,0:07:57.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The trip from Minayo{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s beauty salon...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.53,0:08:01.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To the garbage collection point where the body was found is in a direct line and they're in close proximity.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.58,0:08:06.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bit she went from there in the exact opposite direction to shop at this convenience store.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.13,0:08:08.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That means...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.05,0:08:11.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The remaining time that made it possible to commit the crime was short...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.34,0:08:17.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How could she have moved the body of a 90 kg man in that time?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.14,0:08:24.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You were hurt, I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.02,0:08:24.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.23,0:08:26.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where did this happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.06,0:08:27.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.98,0:08:30.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That time in the ear when Dad braked suddenly.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.65,0:08:33.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.45,0:08:34.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sudden braking!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.42,0:08:50.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If my reasoning to correct...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.46,0:08:51.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There should be something left behind here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.59,0:08:57.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, it's just as I thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.85,0:09:00.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I understand almost everything now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.77,0:09:05.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How a man was dropped into the depths of the Abyss.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.27,0:09:08.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That terrible trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.53,0:09:16.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This guy again?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.24,0:09:19.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Haven't I been saying it the entire time?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.70,0:09:23.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's impossible for Hasaka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} to have committed the crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.70,0:09:25.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, you see, Kisaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.54,0:09:29.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The presumed time of death was between 8:10 PM and 8:30 PM.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.54,0:09:36.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That time when Hasaka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} had left your side, that's still really bugging me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.30,0:09:36.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.38,0:09:40.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not to mention that Hasaka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was Nagasaku{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s former girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.76,0:09:43.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That doesn't have any bearing now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.97,0:09:46.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We checked the video of the security camera.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.81,0:09:50.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For the four minutes between 8:24 and 8:28...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.52,0:09:51.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She was definitely inside the store.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.48,0:09:57.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The time available for her to commit the crime was the four minutes between 8:20 and 8:24 and...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.70,0:10:00.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The two minutes between 8:28 and 8:30.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.70,0:10:02.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In that short amount of time, how could she...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.95,0:10:05.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Have moved the body of a 90 kg man...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.20,0:10:09.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To that garbage collection point on the street two levels below?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.63,0:10:11.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Or is there something else?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.38,0:10:14.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is the reason you're suspicious of her because she's the beautician that I use?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.55,0:10:18.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What kind of talk is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.89,0:10:26.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.10,0:10:28.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're being too harsh.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.27,0:10:31.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The reason Dad came here today was...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.77,0:10:33.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Actually to pick you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.77,0:10:36.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I figured that out a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.57,0:10:40.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In that case, why?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.61,0:10:43.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because he's been playing dumb about it and hasn't said a single word to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.66,0:10:45.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm doing it just to irritate him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.79,0:10:48.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.04,0:10:50.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shouldn't you ask him about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.50,0:10:52.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You could say, "Did you come to pick me up?"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.34,0:10:54.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.34,0:10:56.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You want me to flirt with that mustached old man?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.63,0:10:58.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Absolutely...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.39,0:11:04.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hasaka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.31,0:11:05.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.85,0:11:08.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just to make sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.10,0:11:10.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Will you allow us to search inside your place?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.52,0:11:15.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We refuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.98,0:11:18.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Article 35 of the Constitution.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.28,0:11:23.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Everyone has the right to refuse access to their homes, official documents, as well as their personal belongings...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.70,0:11:27.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As well as the any investigatory search or seizure thereof.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.74,0:11:32.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And, except in the case of arrest, that right can be asserted on the basis of any legitimate reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.96,0:11:38.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Moreover, it cannot be violated unless there's a warrant that explicitly states the places to be searched and the items to be seized.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.09,0:11:41.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you really must search...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.38,0:11:47.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can you please provide us with an arrest warrant or one that permits search and seizure issued by the court?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.39,0:11:49.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,B-But, you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.77,0:11:54.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, since she couldn't have committed the crime, I suppose that would be impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.86,0:11:56.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.07,0:11:59.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nicely done, Lawyer Kisaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.40,0:12:01.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was definitely right...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.78,0:12:04.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To choose you to be the witness for my alibi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.12,0:12:08.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, what if I show you proof?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.66,0:12:12.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Proof that she was capable of performing the crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.04,0:12:20.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're talking like you could really prove it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.01,0:12:21.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, just now...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.09,0:12:23.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It wasn't me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.85,0:12:36.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's appeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.44,0:12:39.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sleeping Kogoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.94,0:12:44.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm glad that Professor Agasa made me this spare voice-changing necktie.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.82,0:12:45.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait a moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.70,0:12:50.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Didn't you just say, "It wasn't me" or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.74,0:12:51.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, that's because...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.25,0:12:57.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was saying it's not just me who can explain a trick that's this simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.79,0:12:59.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The trick Hasaka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} used when she murdered Nagasaku{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.21,0:13:04.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In order to toss him to the garbage collection point two levels below.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.43,0:13:13.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.56,0:13:16.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could you prepare some strong fishing line, like that used for big game fishing...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.52,0:13:19.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And some cement bags to stand in for the victim?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.48,0:13:21.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Takagi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.03,0:13:22.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.49,0:13:27.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, before you do that, please take some photographs.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.24,0:13:28.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Photographs?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.41,0:13:32.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of the thing right above the garbage collection point where we discovered the body...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.50,0:13:36.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The post of that guardrail.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.08,0:13:38.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As well as what's at the turn to the convenience store...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.79,0:13:42.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The thin strip on the post of the road sign.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.84,0:13:44.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And what is on the road near that sign...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.17,0:13:47.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The small pile of rubbish that's been collected into a circle.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.27,0:13:55.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.14,0:13:56.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The preparations are complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.60,0:13:58.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In that case, shall we begin?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.31,0:14:02.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please take down the chair that's been placed on the table over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.02,0:14:06.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That chair was the first thing that I found suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.45,0:14:09.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,On that chair...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.66,0:14:12.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The seat's been extended to the highest point, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.29,0:14:13.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.66,0:14:17.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Minayo{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} is a well-organized person.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.87,0:14:20.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The old newspapers and old magazines have been carefully separated...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.75,0:14:23.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the cardboard has been folded up and tied.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.67,0:14:25.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Despite that, there was that chair...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.51,0:14:30.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,With its seat left like that extended to the highest point that caught my notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.22,0:14:32.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I just happened to carelessly leave it that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.31,0:14:36.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In order to successfully perform this trick...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.27,0:14:39.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was necessary for that chair to be left extended.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.73,0:14:43.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shall we begin to reproduce that trick now?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.52,0:14:44.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Detective Takagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.65,0:14:45.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.86,0:14:49.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To start with, tie the fishing line you prepared onto the shaft of the chair.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.03,0:14:52.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Knot if firmly so that it won't come undone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.91,0:14:55.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next, take the end of that line...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.24,0:14:58.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You see the garbage collection point where the body was discovered?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.58,0:15:03.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Loop it around the back of the post of the guardrail directly that's directly in front of it...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.04,0:15:04.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.38,0:15:10.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now, for the length of the line running from the chair to the guardrail...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.97,0:15:16.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Adjust it so that it's roughly the same as the distance from the back of the beauty salon to the road with the convenience store.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.10,0:15:20.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, tie it to the rear of the scooter that's parked at the back door.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.52,0:15:22.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's all done.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.60,0:15:23.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well then...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.61,0:15:26.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tie another section of line to the rear of the scooter.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.94,0:15:28.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For the length this time...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.57,0:15:33.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Make it a bit longer than the distance from the guardrail to the street with the convenience store...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.16,0:15:35.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And tie it to the shaft of the chair.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.78,0:15:36.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Finally...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.66,0:15:40.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Place the cement bags we're using as a substitute for the body and the setup is complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.04,0:15:45.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, all you have to do is head to the convenience store on the scooter.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.34,0:15:50.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are the preparations all ready on your end?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.84,0:15:51.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.93,0:15:54.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just as you instructed, we've cleared out all the onlookers.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.22,0:15:56.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good, got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.81,0:15:57.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Takagi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.64,0:15:58.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Go for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.64,0:16:03.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Start off slowly at first so that the cement bags don't fall...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.23,0:16:05.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then begin accelerating little by little.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.61,0:16:06.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.50,0:16:28.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector Megure!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.59,0:16:31.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The cement bags really did fall into the garbage collection point!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.13,0:16:33.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.38,0:16:37.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When the chair collided forcibly with the guardrail...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.55,0:16:39.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,According to the law of inertia...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.14,0:16:41.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The body that was placed on the chair went flying...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.47,0:16:44.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And it fell down into the garbage collection point two levels below.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.23,0:16:48.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Also, the thread we tied on at first snapped due to the shock of the collision.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.90,0:16:51.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you keep going on the scooter up to the convenience store...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.28,0:16:58.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The line we tied on later pulls the chair, and that's how it was returned to the alley.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.54,0:17:02.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The law of inertia, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.66,0:17:07.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, the origin of the "whack", "thud" and "klink klink" sounds we heard...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.29,0:17:08.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was from this, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.92,0:17:13.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, those thin stripes on the guardrail and the road sign...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.63,0:17:15.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Were left by the rubbing of the line then.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.13,0:17:17.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.18,0:17:19.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If the body was sitting on the chair...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.22,0:17:22.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think the legs would have gotten caught in the guardrail and it wouldn't have flown over like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.14,0:17:24.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To ensure that didn't happen...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.68,0:17:27.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The victim was likely placed with his legs crossed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.06,0:17:33.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The reason the chair was extended to the highest point was so that the body could clear the guardrail.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.90,0:17:36.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, what caused the rubbish to collect in a circle on the road?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.28,0:17:39.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When Minayo{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was returning from the convenience store...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.28,0:17:43.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The dangling string swept up rubbish from the road.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.75,0:17:46.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The reason the scooter's engine stalled was...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.17,0:17:51.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Due to the sudden braking from when the chair collided with the guardrail.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.84,0:17:53.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where's the proof?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.67,0:17:56.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The proof that I killed him?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.80,0:17:59.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aren't you being awfully mean treating, me like a criminal without any proof?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.51,0:18:01.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right, Kisaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.31,0:18:07.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That proof is, perhaps...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.48,0:18:12.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.19,0:18:13.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's waking up at the most crucial part!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.70,0:18:18.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's the proof?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.70,0:18:20.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Proof?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.07,0:18:23.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Provision 239 of the civil code.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.79,0:18:28.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you gain possession of unowned property with the purpose of establishing ownership...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.54,0:18:30.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then your ownership is established.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.71,0:18:31.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In other words...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.46,0:18:33.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Once garbage has been thrown away at the garbage collection point...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.88,0:18:38.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If there is someone in need of it, then it can become that person's property.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.84,0:18:43.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If we check the garbage that you took with you to the convenience store, then we'll know, won't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.18,0:18:45.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you were the culprit...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.85,0:18:49.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then the bloodstained cape and towel that the victim was wearing at the time of the crime...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.89,0:18:52.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You would have wanted to dispose of them immediately by way of the garbage.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.53,0:19:03.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your reaction tells me that we don't even need to bother checking.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.53,0:19:05.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's disappointing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.04,0:19:09.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That you would use me in order to create your alibi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.04,0:19:12.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Most likely...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.21,0:19:14.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You asked Nagasaku{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} to come to your place before I arrived...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.50,0:19:19.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then you used the ten minutes when my coloring was setting...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.30,0:19:20.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To murder Nagasaku{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.43,0:19:24.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, you used the trick we just saw to toss away the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.76,0:19:26.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.72,0:19:28.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When you collected the string...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.39,0:19:31.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You were in a hurry and forgot to lower the height of the chair.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.94,0:19:35.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The reason you threw the body onto the garbage collection point was...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.44,0:19:37.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So someone would discover it quickly for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.48,0:19:41.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since you didn't want a wide window for the estimated time of death.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.82,0:19:44.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you really resent Nagasaku{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} that much?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.33,0:19:47.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I didn't really resent him that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.20,0:19:49.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The one I hated was...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.20,0:19:51.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That talent he was engaged to.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.58,0:19:54.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He and I had a fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.29,0:19:55.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,During the short time when we weren't seeing each other...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.75,0:19:56.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She approached him...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.00,0:19:59.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then she got engaged to him instead!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.51,0:20:00.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.34,0:20:01.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why him?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.88,0:20:02.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You don't understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.43,0:20:07.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When he debuted as a fighter, he had short black hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.14,0:20:11.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The one who made him change to medium length blond hair was her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.02,0:20:13.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was completely unbearable!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.52,0:20:18.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His entire appearance had been changed in accordance with that woman's orders!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.44,0:20:19.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.57,0:20:23.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That look of satisfaction on his face...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.03,0:20:26.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, couldn't you have just left him alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.78,0:20:28.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I had to cut his hair for the rest of his life.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.41,0:20:32.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's what I promised him when I became a beautician.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.33,0:20:36.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I didn't want anyone else to cut it...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.13,0:20:38.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And I didn't want to cut it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.42,0:20:41.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, this is all I could do...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.30,0:20:50.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, we can discuss the rest at the station.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.89,0:20:51.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Takagi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.36,0:21:00.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You should be careful too, Kisaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.86,0:21:04.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fighting with him for silly reasons...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.78,0:21:06.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your petty competition...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.78,0:21:09.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There are some things that can't be mended.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.91,0:21:11.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.12,0:21:15.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it's really too bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.79,0:21:19.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now I won't be able to listen to Kisaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} telling fond stories about her husband any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.59,0:21:22.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fond stories?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.09,0:21:23.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.17,0:21:26.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Those weren't fond stories.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.72,0:21:27.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.26,0:21:30.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't be silly.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.31,0:21:31.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How could it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.93,0:21:33.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.28,0:23:09.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.41,0:23:11.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Does that bother you?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.87,0:23:17.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You really made 1200 thousand yen betting on a dark horse?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.70,0:23:19.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wow, congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.54,0:23:21.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll raise a toast tonight!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.37,0:23:22.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're already drinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.38,0:23:25.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.71,0:23:29.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That phone call?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.97,0:23:34.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That call was from my horse-racing buddy who's been calling me the whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.85,0:23:37.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's been pestering me to go drinking because he made a killing!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.52,0:23:45.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.48,0:23:48.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.40,0:23:52.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How did the case turn out?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.45,0:23:54.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.16,0:23:57.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have no idea either.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.08,0:24:03.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eisuke{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-niichan{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.29,0:24:04.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You came back to school?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.46,0:24:06.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.00,0:24:07.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was reinstated today.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.55,0:24:09.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I still don't know who it is, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.01,0:24:12.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What I think about this situation is that...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.84,0:24:15.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's an FBI agent observing Hondou Eisuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.10,0:24:22.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.14,0:24:23.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Him...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.02,0:24:30.03,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,BLIND SPOT IN THE KARAOKE BOX\N(PART ONE)
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.74,0:24:32.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next Conan's Hint
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.99,0:24:34.99,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Hondou Eisuke
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.36,0:24:37.28,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Next time the scene is at a karaoke box.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.28,0:24:38.28,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Even if I'm off key...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.28,0:24:39.41,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,My reasoning is pitched right!
